```
STRIPE_API_KEY=YOUR_STRIPE_API_KEY
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@host:port/dbname
```

This code provides a basic e-commerce functionality for a music instruments website. It includes user registration and login, product catalog, shopping cart, and checkout with payment processing using Stripe. The code is structured into separate files for models, routes, and the main application. It uses Flask as the web framework, Flask-SQLAlchemy for database operations, and Flask-Login for user authentication. The Stripe API is used for payment processing. The code includes proper error handling and comments for better understanding.